{"tid":1708063,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"突然有諗法，係咪應該要鼓勵埋和理非捐血？","createTime":"2019-11-11T12:51:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T12:35:41.000Z","uid":263668,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e60e7e78734e217b5516604ef0488579dbe79e81","tid":1708063,"uid":263668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:51:40.000Z","msg":"頭先睇新聞見到話今朝手足輸左3L血，可想而知我地又一城爆頭手足，梓樂都一定用左唔少。而家傷亡慘重嘅往往係我地手足，如果我地捐血，佢地按理都會受益多過藍絲廢老死黑警。<br />\n<br />\n捐完血唔多唔少會影響體能（我會虛一輪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />超弱雞），所以唔建議前線去捐，而希望鼓勵和理非喺可以嘅情況下喺呢方面都幫幫手。"},{"pid":"8808a1d35e9376223d0fbb254fc9da79be1b1ee3","tid":1708063,"uid":9,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:54:56.000Z","msg":"前兩日捐完"},{"pid":"058c1d1190bdd5810dcb15c64b5d466e278ddd7a","tid":1708063,"uid":263668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:00:15.000Z","msg":"想文宣加埋捐血入去和理非日常可以幫到手嘅事度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a8b890675bcf43cd043491e16a10d114a777ad4","tid":1708063,"uid":190239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:42:02.000Z","msg":"想問係咪捐紅十字會？"},{"pid":"96392aeb8653d2d2a0d2b9d30572119aa225ad02","tid":1708063,"uid":251435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:47:58.000Z","msg":"之前都咁諗 但唔知近期聞過tg捐唔捐得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0eac320ffe9251be38e2654f2f2977997168d70","tid":1708063,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:50:51.000Z","msg":"有冇得淨係捐畀手足 <br />\n依家捐血嗰啲好似好多都係比支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b92fa5779c13b325b998c9cff1110537944790cc","tid":1708063,"uid":263668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a8b890675bcf43cd043491e16a10d114a777ad4","tid":1708063,"uid":190239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score